title: Fire and Ice
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mongolian grill. Choice of different vegetable and a few soy meats for your stir fry. Has a separate section on grill for cooking vegan - let your cook know. Many vegetarian sauces. Approximately 9 of 13 appetizers have a vegetarian option. Has Wi-Fi and lounge. Large space with video screen.
